title: GameHouse - Text Twist 2 - New Word Game [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
TextTwist 2


Twist again with TextTwist 2, the incredible sequel to one 
of the most popular word games of all time. Shuffle letters 
to form words in three all-new game modes and two of your favorites! 
Find the word that uses all of the letters as fast as you can in 
Lightning mode, complete a crossword puzzle using a limited number of 
letters in Crossword mode, or try the new daily challenge in Word of 
the Day mode featuring a new group of letters every day! For classic 
twisting fun try your hand at the original Timed and Untimed modes. 
Super TextTwist revolutionized casual word games. Now, TextTwist 2 
takes it to the next level. Featuring 25,000 words to find, amazing 
new graphics, and nearly endless family fun, TextTwist 2 is 
a must-have for word game fans. 

Thanks to TAC-CM
